descriptionHTML:
TimeLine Techno Blue modern analog interactive watch face for Android wear.

Features of the watch face:

- Date
- Second time
- Battery
- Weather
- Dual battery
- Color customization
- 2 Ambient modes
- Interactive mode (change color, open app, change dials)
- And other settings

-Weather information is provided by http://openweathermap.org

Compatible with:

- Android Wear devices
